[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":614},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231002\u002F2297973079\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231002\u002F2297973079\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231002\u002F2297973079\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231002\u002F2297973079\u002F":589,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231002\u002F2297973079\u002F":598},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2023\u002F10\u002F02\u002Fday-18-getting-to-know-crontab\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":572,"date":573,"description":25,"extension":574,"lang":575,"meta":576,"navigation":577,"path":578,"readingMinutes":579,"seo":580,"standalone":581,"stem":582,"tags":583,"tldr":586,"updated":573,"url":587,"__hash__":588},"content\u002F《Node.js 不負責系列：把前端人員當作後端來用，就算是前端也能嘗試寫的後端～原來 Node.js 可以做這麼多事～》\u002FDay18-初識-Crontab.md","Day18 - 初識 Crontab","2297973079",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":566},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,30,33,36,39,64,68,71,74,77,105,111,114,133,136,139,150,153,156,177,180,191,194,197,218,220,231,234,253,255,266,273,276,295,297,308,311,330,332,343,350,353,372,375,400,403,408,415,431,434,443,446,449,511,514,538,545,548,559,562],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"Crontab","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fisray_notarray_calendar_07b56f00-70a2-4d40-825f-e0f29a0c5008.png",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"看到現在，你也應該學了不少知識了，你應該會發現有些系統好像都會「自動」去做某些事情，所以接下來將會來介紹例行性工作排程 (crontab) 這個東西。",[20,27,29],{"id":28},"crontab-是什麼","Crontab 是什麼？",[12,31,32],{},"不知道你有沒有一種習慣，也就是固定每天要做的事情，例如說每天早上起床後都會刷牙洗臉，或是每天晚上睡覺前都會刷牙洗臉，這些事情都是你每天都會做的事情，而且都是固定的時間去做，這就是一種工作排程。",[12,34,35],{},"很難有感覺吧？畢竟這舉例太過於生活化了，讓我換另一個方式去形容，假設你今天是一個公司的老闆，你每年可能都要替公司舉辦團康、員工旅遊、開發會議、年終獎金發放等等，這些事情都是你每年都會做的事情，但這些事情實在有夠多，依照人腦來講，你就很難記得每一件事情要在什麼時候做，所以你就會把這些行程寫在 Google 日曆上，接著 Google 日曆就會在你設定的時間提醒你，這就是一種工作排程。",[12,37,38],{},"那麼為什麼會提到工作排程呢？因為我們實戰開發上其實也會用到這個技巧，所以這一篇我們將會來介紹 Node.js 中該如何實現 Crontab 的功能。",[40,41,42],"blockquote",{},[12,43,44,48,49,53,54,57,58,60,61,63],{},[45,46,47],"strong",{},"Note","\n題外話一下，Linux 中有兩種排程工具，一種是 ",[50,51,52],"code",{},"at","，另一種就是 ",[50,55,56],{},"crontab","，而 ",[50,59,56],{}," 是比較常用的，所以這一篇就以 ",[50,62,56],{}," 來做介紹；Linux 一個自由和開放原始碼的類 UNIX 作業系統。",[20,65,67],{"id":66},"crontab-格式","Crontab 格式",[12,69,70],{},"你以為馬上就可以來認識 Crontab 了嗎？",[12,72,73],{},"不，你還得先認識 Crontab 的格式，因為 Crontab 的格式是一個很重要的概念，所以你必須要先了解它。",[12,75,76],{},"首先，我們先來看一下 Crontab 的範例格式：",[78,79,84],"pre",{"className":80,"code":81,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},"language-bash shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","* * * * *\n","bash","",[50,85,86],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,88,91,95,98,100,102],"span",{"class":89,"line":90},"line",1,[87,92,94],{"class":93},"sWyjQ","*",[87,96,97],{"class":93}," *",[87,99,97],{"class":93},[87,101,97],{"class":93},[87,103,104],{"class":93}," *\n",[12,106,107],{},[15,108],{"alt":109,"src":110},"呼攏你","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002F1693486896933.png",[12,112,113],{},"oh，別擔心，我並沒有耍你的意思，這個格式其實就是 Crontab 的格式，而這個格式又可以分成五個部分，分別是：",[115,116,117,121,124,127,130],"ul",{},[118,119,120],"li",{},"分鐘 (Minute)",[118,122,123],{},"小時 (Hour)",[118,125,126],{},"日期 (Day)",[118,128,129],{},"月份 (Month)",[118,131,132],{},"星期 (Week)",[12,134,135],{},"那麼以前面剛剛寫的範例格式來講，在 Crontab 中的意思就是「每分鐘、每小時、每天、每月、每週」，也就是說，這個格式就是代表每分鐘都會執行一次。",[12,137,138],{},"假設現在是 2023\u002F08\u002F31 21:12 那就代表著，這個 Crontab 會在...",[115,140,141,144,147],{},[118,142,143],{},"2023\u002F08\u002F31 21:13",[118,145,146],{},"2023\u002F08\u002F31 21:14",[118,148,149],{},"2023\u002F08\u002F31 21:15...",[12,151,152],{},"以此類推，每分鐘都會執行一次。",[12,154,155],{},"那麼如果我們希望每半小時執行一次的話，那就可以這樣寫：",[78,157,159],{"className":80,"code":158,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},"*\u002F30 * * * *\n",[50,160,161],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,162,163,165,169,171,173,175],{"class":89,"line":90},[87,164,94],{"class":93},[87,166,168],{"class":167},"sMAXC","\u002F30 ",[87,170,94],{"class":93},[87,172,97],{"class":93},[87,174,97],{"class":93},[87,176,104],{"class":93},[12,178,179],{},"這樣會跑的時間就會是...",[115,181,182,185,188],{},[118,183,184],{},"2023\u002F08\u002F31 21:30",[118,186,187],{},"2023\u002F08\u002F31 22:00",[118,189,190],{},"2023\u002F08\u002F31 22:30...",[12,192,193],{},"以此類推，每半小時都會執行一次。",[12,195,196],{},"那如果我們期望是每天的 12:00 執行一次的話，那就可以這樣寫：",[78,198,200],{"className":80,"code":199,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},"0 12 * * *\n",[50,201,202],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,203,204,208,212,214,216],{"class":89,"line":90},[87,205,207],{"class":206},"s_sBn","0",[87,209,211],{"class":210},"sCcAr"," 12",[87,213,97],{"class":210},[87,215,97],{"class":210},[87,217,104],{"class":210},[12,219,179],{},[115,221,222,225,228],{},[118,223,224],{},"2023\u002F09\u002F01 12:00",[118,226,227],{},"2023\u002F09\u002F02 12:00",[118,229,230],{},"2023\u002F09\u002F03 12:00...",[12,232,233],{},"當然，還有一種很特殊的狀況，也就是每個月的一號的下午三點執行一次，那就可以這樣寫：",[78,235,237],{"className":80,"code":236,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},"0 15 1 * *\n",[50,238,239],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,240,241,243,246,249,251],{"class":89,"line":90},[87,242,207],{"class":206},[87,244,245],{"class":210}," 15",[87,247,248],{"class":210}," 1",[87,250,97],{"class":210},[87,252,104],{"class":210},[12,254,179],{},[115,256,257,260,263],{},[118,258,259],{},"2023\u002F09\u002F01 15:00",[118,261,262],{},"2023\u002F10\u002F01 15:00",[118,264,265],{},"2023\u002F11\u002F01 15:00...",[40,267,268],{},[12,269,270,272],{},[45,271,47],{},"\ncrontab 的時間是採用 24 小時制。",[12,274,275],{},"那如果我們期望是特定日期呢？crontab 也做得到，例如一年一度的聖誕節，那就可以這樣寫：",[78,277,279],{"className":80,"code":278,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},"0 0 25 12 *\n",[50,280,281],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,282,283,285,288,291,293],{"class":89,"line":90},[87,284,207],{"class":206},[87,286,287],{"class":210}," 0",[87,289,290],{"class":210}," 25",[87,292,211],{"class":210},[87,294,104],{"class":210},[12,296,179],{},[115,298,299,302,305],{},[118,300,301],{},"2023\u002F12\u002F25 00:00",[118,303,304],{},"2024\u002F12\u002F25 00:00",[118,306,307],{},"2025\u002F12\u002F25 00:00...",[12,309,310],{},"很有趣吧？那如果今天是希望每個禮拜三早上九點呢？那就可以這樣寫：",[78,312,314],{"className":80,"code":313,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},"0 9 * * 3\n",[50,315,316],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,317,318,320,323,325,327],{"class":89,"line":90},[87,319,207],{"class":206},[87,321,322],{"class":210}," 9",[87,324,97],{"class":210},[87,326,97],{"class":210},[87,328,329],{"class":210}," 3\n",[12,331,179],{},[115,333,334,337,340],{},[118,335,336],{},"2023\u002F09\u002F06 09:00",[118,338,339],{},"2023\u002F09\u002F13 09:00",[118,341,342],{},"2023\u002F09\u002F20 09:00...",[40,344,345],{},[12,346,347,349],{},[45,348,47],{},"\ncrontab 的星期是從 0 開始，0 代表星期日，1 代表星期一，以此類推。",[12,351,352],{},"那如果今天是希望每個禮拜一到禮拜五早上九點呢？那就可以這樣寫：",[78,354,356],{"className":80,"code":355,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},"0 9 * * 1-5\n",[50,357,358],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,359,360,362,364,366,368],{"class":89,"line":90},[87,361,207],{"class":206},[87,363,322],{"class":210},[87,365,97],{"class":210},[87,367,97],{"class":210},[87,369,371],{"class":370},"sTRMh"," 1-5\n",[12,373,374],{},"超有趣的吧？crontab 其實非常的靈活，你可以依照你的需求去做設定，而且 crontab 也有一些特殊的符號，例如...",[115,376,377,382,388,394],{},[118,378,379,381],{},[50,380,94],{},"：代表任意值",[118,383,384,387],{},[50,385,386],{},",","：代表分隔符號",[118,389,390,393],{},[50,391,392],{},"-","：代表範圍",[118,395,396,399],{},[50,397,398],{},"\u002F","：代表間隔",[12,401,402],{},"因此 crontab 也會被稱為「crontab 計畫表達式」，因為撰寫方式其實與表達式很像，底下我也提供一個簡單的圖來說明：",[12,404,405],{},[15,406],{"alt":56,"src":407},"https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fcrontab_img.jpg",[12,409,410,411,414],{},"當然，crontab 還有一些特殊的符號，例如 ",[50,412,413],{},"@reboot","，這個符號代表著系統開機時就會執行，用法其實很簡單，例如我們原本是寫這樣：",[78,416,417],{"className":80,"code":355,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},[50,418,419],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,420,421,423,425,427,429],{"class":89,"line":90},[87,422,207],{"class":206},[87,424,322],{"class":210},[87,426,97],{"class":210},[87,428,97],{"class":210},[87,430,371],{"class":370},[12,432,433],{},"那如果我們希望系統開機時就會執行的話，就可以這樣寫：",[78,435,437],{"className":80,"code":436,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},"@reboot\n",[50,438,439],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,440,441],{"class":89,"line":90},[87,442,436],{"class":206},[12,444,445],{},"直接把原本的格式替換掉就可以了。",[12,447,448],{},"當然這些是屬於比較特殊的排程，其他還有...",[115,450,451,460,468,477,486,495,502],{},[118,452,453,456,457],{},[50,454,455],{},"@yearly","：每年的 1 月 1 日 00:00 執行一次，如同 ",[50,458,459],{},"0 0 1 1 *",[118,461,462,465,466],{},[50,463,464],{},"@annually","：同 ",[50,467,455],{},[118,469,470,473,474],{},[50,471,472],{},"@monthly","：每月的 1 日 00:00 執行一次，如同 ",[50,475,476],{},"0 0 1 * *",[118,478,479,482,483],{},[50,480,481],{},"@weekly","：每週的星期日 00:00 執行一次，如同 ",[50,484,485],{},"0 0 * * 0",[118,487,488,491,492],{},[50,489,490],{},"@daily","：每天 00:00 執行一次，如同 ",[50,493,494],{},"0 0 * * *",[118,496,497,465,500],{},[50,498,499],{},"@midnight",[50,501,490],{},[118,503,504,507,508],{},[50,505,506],{},"@hourly","：每小時 00 分執行一次，如同 ",[50,509,510],{},"0 * * * *",[12,512,513],{},"那麼如果你是在 Linux 系統上的話，該怎麼執行你要執行的命令呢？其實很簡單，只需要在 crontab 的時間格式後面加上你要執行的命令就可以了，例如：",[78,515,517],{"className":80,"code":516,"language":82,"meta":83,"style":83},"0 9 * * 1-5 node \u002Fhome\u002Fithelp\u002Fithelp.js\n",[50,518,519],{"__ignoreMap":83},[87,520,521,523,525,527,529,532,535],{"class":89,"line":90},[87,522,207],{"class":206},[87,524,322],{"class":210},[87,526,97],{"class":210},[87,528,97],{"class":210},[87,530,531],{"class":370}," 1-5",[87,533,534],{"class":370}," node",[87,536,537],{"class":370}," \u002Fhome\u002Fithelp\u002Fithelp.js\n",[12,539,540,541,544],{},"這樣子就可以在每週一到週五的早上九點執行 ",[50,542,543],{},"\u002Fhome\u002Fithelp\u002Fithelp.js"," 這個檔案了。",[12,546,547],{},"那麼關於 Linux 的部分我就不細講了，畢竟這不是我這一次的主題範圍內。",[12,549,550,551,558],{},"最後，如果你覺得 crontab 格式很難記的話，其實你可以到 ",[552,553,557],"a",{"href":554,"rel":555},"https:\u002F\u002Fcrontab.guru\u002F",[556],"nofollow","crontab guru"," 網站上去做測試，這個網站可以幫你解析 crontab 的格式，並且會告訴你這個 crontab 會在什麼時候執行哩～",[12,560,561],{},"那麼這一篇也差不多要結束了，剩下的我們下一篇見囉～",[563,564,565],"style",{},"html pre.shiki code .sWyjQ, html code.shiki .sWyjQ{--shiki-default:#FF9492}html .default .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html .shiki span {color: var(--shiki-default);background: var(--shiki-default-bg);font-style: var(--shiki-default-font-style);font-weight: var(--shiki-default-font-weight);text-decoration: var(--shiki-default-text-decoration);}html pre.shiki code .sMAXC, html code.shiki .sMAXC{--shiki-default:#F0F3F6}html pre.shiki code .s_sBn, html code.shiki .s_sBn{--shiki-default:#FFB757}html pre.shiki code .sCcAr, html code.shiki .sCcAr{--shiki-default:#91CBFF}html pre.shiki code .sTRMh, html code.shiki .sTRMh{--shiki-default:#ADDCFF}",{"title":83,"searchDepth":567,"depth":567,"links":568},2,[569,570,571],{"id":22,"depth":567,"text":22},{"id":28,"depth":567,"text":29},{"id":66,"depth":567,"text":67},"Nodejs","2023-10-02 00:00:01","md","zh-Hant",{},true,"\u002Fnode.js-node.js\u002Fday18-crontab","3",{"title":6,"description":25},false,"《Node.js 不負責系列：把前端人員當作後端來用，就算是前端也能嘗試寫的後端～原來 Node.js 可以做這麼多事～》\u002FDay18-初識-Crontab",[584,585],"Node.js","《Node.js 不負責系列：把前端人員當作後端來用，就算是前端也能嘗試寫的後端～原來 Node.js 可以做這麼多事～》",null,"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231002\u002F2297973079\u002F","wFa3cb13dyejIWouLZruEAs_FSzAybyCgRlIDQjnHF0",{"newer":590,"older":594},{"url":591,"title":592,"date":593},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231003\u002F1830434204\u002F","Day19 - Crontab + Node.js","2023-10-03 00:00:01",{"url":595,"title":596,"date":597},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231001\u002F2119244773\u002F","Day17 - 續談爬蟲（下）","2023-10-01 00:00:01",[599,604,609],{"url":600,"title":601,"date":602,"readingMinutes":603},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20260113\u002F3115395907\u002F","真是受夠開多個終端機執行多個指令了！來用 concurrently 吧","2026-01-13 09:45:28","2",{"url":605,"title":606,"date":607,"readingMinutes":608},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20250313\u002F3008873732\u002F","六角專題班學習組電商 API 之完整教學","2025-03-13 09:13:26","11",{"url":610,"title":611,"date":612,"readingMinutes":613},"\u002Fnodejs\u002F20241225\u002F794319627\u002F","PM2 是 Process Manager 不是 PM2.5！","2024-12-25 10:31:33","6",1784013090839]